# Here are a few trees that are native to Ithaca

* Pinus strobus
* Acer saccharum
* Acer rubrum
* Acer negundo
* Nyssa sylvatica
* Quercus alba
* Quercus velutina
* Quercus montana
* Quercus coccinea
* Quercus bicolor
* Liriodendron tulipifera
